1. Mobile speedpage is 97, and desktop one is 98. To achieve these results I:
-	minified CSS
-	inlined CSS
-	minified JS
-	inlined JS
-	unblocked all critical resources
-	optimized pictures
-	optimized media prints
-	altered font style (moved it to CSS)

2. To make FPS be 60 or higher I:
- moved weighty computations outside of the for loop
- limited the number of pizzas; instead of 200 pizzas the number is limited by the screen parameters. 
Average time to generate last 10 frames is less than 0.5 ms now.
